<view class="container">
  <view class='shopP_box mb20' >
      <view class='shopP_tit'>平台承诺</view>
      <view class='shopP_txt'>
        <text>1、平台所售商品，顾客均可到当地商家下线门店体验。</text>
        <text>2、顾客在门店体验过程中不收任何费用，以期给予客户最好的服务</text>
      </view>
  </view>
  <view class='shopP_box mb20' >
      <view class='shopP_tit'>收货方式</view>
      <view class='shopP_img'>
        <image src='/lib/images/shopP_pic.jpg'  mode="widthFix"></image>
      </view>
  </view>
  <view class='shopP_box' >
      <view class='shopP_list'>
        <view>
          <image src='/lib/images/shopP_icon1.jpg'  mode="widthFix"></image>
