          <text class='shopP_t2'>先体验,后购买.平台所售商品,均可到当地门店免费体验.  </text>
        </view>
        <view>
          <image src='/lib/images/shopP_icon3.jpg'  mode="widthFix"></image>
          <text class='shopP_t1'>高效配送</text>
          <text class='shopP_t2'>专业配送,一站式送货到家 </text>
        </view>
        <view>
          <image src='/lib/images/shopP_icon4.jpg'  mode="widthFix"></image>
          <text class='shopP_t1'>售后保障</text>
          <text class='shopP_t2'>售后服务均由合作门店线下提供,让您售后无忧 </text>
        </view>
      </view>
  </view>
